1
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:30,130
That foolish saint doesn't even know.

2
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:31,390
Her brother's lineage

3
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:33,630
is now down to just a few old, weak, and sick individuals,

4
00:00:33,630 --> 00:00:35,490
waiting to die in the Sin Village.

5
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:37,630
Her brother's lineage

6
00:00:38,530 --> 00:00:40,530
is down to the old, weak, and sick.

7
00:00:40,930 --> 00:00:41,900
Get lost.

8
00:00:42,530 --> 00:00:44,060
I want to see the Inspector.

9
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:47,060
Lord Inspector,

10
00:00:47,230 --> 00:00:48,290
about the Luo clan,

11
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:50,060
aren't we being too ruthless?

12
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:51,960
What if Luo Jinghong finds out?

13
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,760
What are you afraid of?

14
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,160
That martial arts fanatic, Luo Jinghong,

15
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:54,960
is obsessed with the Dao.

16
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,660
She's been defending against the demons at the frontlines

17
00:00:56,660 --> 00:00:57,960
and hasn't moved an inch for thousands of years.

18
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,030
There's no way she knows.

19
00:00:59,030 --> 00:01:00,660
And so what if she finds out?

20
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:01,800
The Luo clan becoming a sin clan

21
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,830
and being exiled to the Sin Village

22
00:01:02,830 --> 00:01:04,730
is the will of the great ancient clans of the Ancestral Court.

23
00:01:04,730 --> 00:01:07,100
The new Human Emperor even issued the decree personally.

24
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:07,700
Does Luo Jinghong

25
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:08,960
dare to defy the decree?

26
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:09,860
If she knows what's good for her,

27
00:01:09,860 --> 00:01:12,100
she'll obediently stay at the Emperor's Pass as a guarding tool.

28
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:12,960
If she doesn't,

29
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:13,830
so what if she's a quasi-emperor?

30
00:01:13,830 --> 00:01:16,200
She's still just a dog of the Ancestral Court.

31
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:18,660
We have plenty of ways to force her to submit.

32
00:01:23,830 --> 00:01:25,160
Where is the Inspector?

33
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:25,960
Luo Jinghong!

34
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:26,960
How dare you be so insolent

35
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:27,960
and abandon your post?

36
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:30,400
Aren't you afraid of being held accountable by His Majesty the Human Emperor?

37
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,260
I am asking you,

38
00:01:31,660 --> 00:01:33,460
what has happened to my Luo clan?

39
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:37,060
You have a death wish!

40
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:38,729
Luo Jinghong,

41
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,330
don't do anything rash!

42
00:01:42,259 --> 00:01:44,600
The Emperor's Pass concerns the safety of the human race.

43
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:46,030
If you leave without permission

44
00:01:46,030 --> 00:01:47,289
and the demons attack,

45
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:49,490
you will be a sinner of the human race!

46
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,800
Tell me the truth,

47
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:56,330
or I'll search your soul right now.

48
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:01,560
Congratulations to the host for successfully changing an important main storyline.

49
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,230
Significantly altered the world's trajectory.

50
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:05,360
Obtained 999 Destiny Fortune Points.

51
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:07,160
Lately, besides accompanying my disciple to visit her relatives,

52
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,460
and swatting an old lecher to death,

53
00:02:08,460 --> 00:02:09,630
I haven't done anything else.

54
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,460
What happened

55
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,800
that could directly alter the main storyline?

56
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,600
A butterfly flaps its wings,

57
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,430
a single thought changes the world.

58
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,200
Karma and destiny,

59
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:14,830
every shift of yin and yang,

60
00:02:14,830 --> 00:02:15,600
all have a reason.

61
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,160
Karma and destiny, how interesting.

62
00:02:25,829 --> 00:02:26,829
Halt!

63
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,060
This is a forbidden area of the human Ancestral Court, the Sin Village.

64
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:30,900
No unauthorized entry.

65
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,360
A chariot pulled by nine dragons.

66
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,700
What a grand display.

67
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:39,400
Could it be some lord from the Ancestral Court coming to inspect?

68
00:02:41,230 --> 00:02:44,060
Who are you to block my master's chariot?

69
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:45,460
Such a young Deity Transformation Realm cultivator!

70
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,990
How old is this little girl?

71
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:48,790
Could her master

72
00:02:49,130 --> 00:02:50,660
be a hidden Great Sage?

73
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,760
May I ask which Great Sage has arrived?

74
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,900
May I know your honorable name?

75
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:55,630
I am a member of the ancient Xiao clan,

76
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:58,030
ordered by the Ancestral Court to guard the Sin Village here.

77
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,829
My master is Gu Lingyuan.

78
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:02,190
Greetings, Emperor Gu.

79
00:03:02,230 --> 00:03:03,160
I deserve to die.

80
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,500
I didn't know you were coming.

81
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:07,430
Gu Lingyuan, that old demon from the Eastern Wasteland and current Quasi-Emperor.

82
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,630
Why would he come to this godforsaken Sin Village?

83
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:10,960
Rumor has it that he is cruel and tyrannical,

84
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,700
wiping out entire families at the slightest provocation.

85
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:13,160
My life is over!

86
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,030
Senior, are you heading to Sin Village?

87
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:20,260
Are you trying to stop me?

88
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,530
N-No,

89
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,090
absolutely not.

90
00:03:37,829 --> 00:03:41,760
Gu Linyuan, the head of the Imperial Gu family, has come to Sin Village!

91
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:50,400
Why did that old demon Gu Lingyuan go to Sin Village?

92
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:53,100
Wasn't he at the Taixuan Holy Land not long ago?

93
00:03:53,130 --> 00:03:55,060
I heard this old demon doesn't have much lifespan left,

94
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:56,800
wandering around carrying an Extreme Dao Emperor Weapon.

95
00:03:56,800 --> 00:04:00,030
Could he be trying to extort our Human Ancestral Court

96
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:01,830
for life-extending treasures?

97
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:31,230
Our Luo family ancestors were an ancient clan!

98
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:34,430
They shed blood and sacrificed their lives for the human race,

99
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:38,890
with countless forebears dying before the Imperial Pass to fend off the demons!

100
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:43,630
But now we are slandered as a sinful clan,

101
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:45,900
suffering torment here.

102
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:49,560
Heavens, open your eyes and see!

103
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:56,530
Old thing, you're about to die and still dare to spout nonsense!

104
00:04:56,659 --> 00:04:58,200
Since you want to die,

105
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,760
I'll grant your wish.

106
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:11,600
Don't hurt my grandpa!

107
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,630
Hahaha!

108
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:18,200
A mere remnant of sinful blood dares to stop me?

109
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,730
Since you want to block for this old thing,

110
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:22,860
I'll beat you up too!
